From: yilisharcs <yilisharcs@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 17 Oct 2025 01:01:45 -0300
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] feat(undo)!: re-sync undo files on external change

Problem: external changes cause the hashes of a file and its undo file
to de-sync, leading to loss of undo history.

Solution: keep a backup of the file to check against if the original has
been changed.

BREAKING CHANGE: modify "backup" to save a copy of the file _after_ it
is written instead of _before_.

